Package: herbivoreTTR
Type: Package
Title: Plant-Herbivore Simulation Using Thornley TTR Model
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: c(
    person(given = "Barry", family = "Brook", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "barry.brook@utas.edu.au"),
    person(given = "GPT-5",  family = "Assistant", role = "ctb")
 )
Description: A quantitative plan-herbivore simulation model ported from C++.
    Implements a Thornley Transport Resistance (TTR) model for plant growth
    coupled with individual-based herbivore foraging behaviour.  This package
    aims to facilitate testing, calibration, and extension within the R ecosystem.
License: MIT
Depends:
    R (>= 3.5)
Encoding: UTF-8
